Source: pedalog-tool
Section: electronics
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Dan Haughey <dan@powwow-pedal-power.org.uk>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), cmake, libpedalog-dev (>= 0.2)
Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Homepage: https://github.com/powwow-pedal-power/pedalog-tool

Package: pedalog-tool
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Command-line tool for reading data from Pedalog devices
 The Pedalog is a device made by Renewable Energy Innovations
 (http://www.re-innovation.co.uk).  It has been specially
 designed to monitor the power and energy generated by pedal
 powered electricity generators.
